		<p class="brief">Theodora Boyadjis is a licensed Architect and LEED Accredited Professional.
		She has 10 years of experience in high end residential, hospitality, restaurant, educational and tenant development projects. Theodora graduated NJIT in 2007 and became LEED AP certified in 2009. Based out of Jersey City, NJ, Theodora works in many areas of NJ including Summit, Short Hills, Madison, Chatham, Jersey City, Randolph and Livingston.</p>
